"""
evaluate_per_sty_v2.py
----------------------
Per-STY evaluation with FORCED COVERAGE across STYs.

Instead of generating 200 random should-match pairs (which cluster in
1-2 STYs), we generate pairs PER STY:
  - For each STY with at least 100 CUIs, generate up to 50 should-match
    pairs by taking CUIs of that STY and finding their 2-hop neighbors
    that ALSO have that STY.
  - Generate 50 should-not-match pairs that touch this STY (1 endpoint
    in STY, other endpoint in different STY, neither in 2-hop neighborhood).

Also fixes the STY name display by handling both TUI codes and full names.

Inputs (notebook globals):
  data, SNOMED_CUIS, TAGS  (TAGS values may be tuple/list/set/frozenset)
"""

import statistics
import random
import time
from collections import defaultdict, Counter


